TextEng: I have Meldanen's silver tooth, taken from his head.
Text: 멜다넨의 은 이빨이 있어, 그의 머리에서 뽑았지.

TextEng: I have the key for Meldanen's warehouse.
Meldanen is dead, but I don't have his tooth. You can trust me.
Text: 멜다넨은 죽었지만, 그의 은 이빨은 없어. 날 믿어.

TextEng: No, I don't... and I don't intend to, either.
Not yet, but I'm working on it.
Where do I find Meldanen's mansion?
Where wizard's place again?
Me have wizard's silver tooth.
Me have key for wizard's warehouse.
He dead... but me gots no proof. You just trust, okay?
Text: 그 죽었어... 근데 나 증거 없어. 그냥 믿어, 알았지?

TextEng: No, me have nothing. Not want to, either.
Text: 아니, 나 아무것도 없어. 할 생각도 없어.

TextEng: No, but me will soon.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> This was pretty risky. Couldn't you give a bit more gold?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 위험이 꽤 컸어. 금화를 조금만 더 줄 수 없겠어?

TextEng: No. Give me more or I'll see what *your* teeth are worth.
Text: 아니. 더 줘. 아니면 *네* 이빨 값이 얼마나 나오는지 보자.

TextEng: The reward will do nicely.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me take big risk. Bigger reward is fairer, no?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 큰 위험 감수했어. 보상 더 큰 게 맞지, 안 그래?

TextEng: Nope. You give more gold or me sell your teeth, maybe.
Text: 아니. 금화 더 줘, 아니면 네 이빨 팔아버릴지도 몰라.

TextEng: Is okay, I guess. Give me now.
Hah! Time for you to die, I guess!
Text: 하! 이제 네가 죽을 차례다, 그치!

TextEng: Fine. Hand it over, then.
Hah!! NOW YOU DIE! RAAAGHHH!!
Give now, then, and I go.
Text: 그럼 지금 줘, 그럼 난 간다.

TextEng: I bring a gift from Meldanen, actually: your death!
Text: 멜다넨이 보낸 선물이 있어, 사실은: 네 죽음!

TextEng: Me have gift from wizard: you die!
Text: 나 마법사한테서 선물 가져왔어: 너 죽어!

TextEng: Not really. I'd rather take it all off your dead body.
Text: 그럴 필요 없지. 차라리 네 시체에서 전부 챙기지.

TextEng: Nah. Me take all gold from you dead body.
Text: 아니. 너 죽은 몸에서 금화 다 가져갈래.

TextEng: Who is this Meldanen?
Who are you?
Who this Meldanen?
Who you?
And who are you, then?
Who you, then?
How do you know there's an actual hoard?
Text: 진짜 비축하고 있다는 걸 어떻게 아는 거지?

TextEng: No, I don't agree with you.
I agree with you, totally.
Leave me out of it, I say.
Regardless, I think you're making trouble and you should stop.
Text: 어쨌든 넌 말썽을 일으키고 있어. 그만두는 게 좋겠어.

TextEng: How you know 'bout hoard?
No, me not agree.
Me agrees with you.
You leaves me out of it.
You make trouble. Me say you stop, now.
Text: 너 문제 만들고 있어. 지금 당장 그만둬.

TextEng: Goodbye.
What, exactly, do you have in mind?
No, I have other obligations.
Forget it!
Me help how?
No, me must do other stuff.
Text: 아니, 나 다른 일 해야 해.

TextEng: Hah! You forget it!
Just how underhanded are we talking, here?
Text: 정확히 어느 정도로 비열한 짓을 하자는 거지?

TextEng: I have no problem with anything of that sort.
I wouldn't perform a task of that nature, no.
What you mean?
Me do task, not care what kind.
Text: 나 그런 일 해. 뭔지 신경 안 써.

TextEng: Me not do that, no.
With the right reward, nothing bothers me.
If me paid good, me not care.
Very well. I will do as you suggest.
I will steal the key, but I will not murder a man.
Perhaps you are right... so long as the reward is.
Text: 아마 네 말이 맞을지도... 보상만 확실하다면.

TextEng: No. I won't do it.
Okay, me will help, then.
Me steal key, but me not murder nobody.
Text: 나 열쇠 훔칠게. 근데 아무도 안 죽여.

TextEng: Okay... but only if me gets lots of coin.
Text: 좋아... 근데 금화 많이 줘야 해.

TextEng: No, me not do it.
Why don't you kill him, then?
Why you no kill him if you think it so great?
Text: 그렇게 좋다 생각하면, 왜 네가 안 죽여?

TextEng: You will kill him or I will?
Text: 네가 죽일 거야, 아니면 내가 할까?

TextEng: You killing or me killing?
I see Meldanen was right. Time for you to die, Formosa.
Text: 멜다넨이 옳았군. 이제 죽을 시간이야, 포르모사.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Could I persuade you to give me some coin up front?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 금화 좀 미리 줄 수 있을까?

TextEng: I want some coin now... or I'll expose you to the local nobles
Text: 지금 금화 좀 줘... 안 그럼 지역 귀족들한테 널 고발할 거야.

TextEng: Very well. I'll do it.
I've changed my mind. This doesn't interest me.
Me see Meldanen right. You die now, Formosa.
Text: 나 멜다넨이 옳았다고 봐. 너 이제 죽어, 포르모사.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Maybe you give some coin now... to be nice, huh?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 지금 금화 좀 줄래... 착하게, 응?

TextEng: Me get coin now... or maybe me talk to other nobles, here. Talk lots.
Text: 나 지금 금화 받아... 아니면 나 여기 다른 귀족들한테 말할 거야. 많이 말해.

TextEng: Okay, me do it.
No, me has changed mind.
To kill you, obviously. Meldanen sends his regards.
Text: 널 죽이러 왔지, 당연히. 멜다넨이 안부 전하래.

TextEng: I just want you to stop making trouble.
Text: 그냥 문제 좀 그만 일으키길 바랄 뿐이야.

TextEng: I'm investigating the plague, and I have some questions.
Text: 역병을 조사 중이야, 물어볼 게 있어.

TextEng: I'm looking for work, actually.
I need some directions.
Me here to kill you. Wizard says hello.
Text: 나 너 죽이러 왔어. 마법사가 안부 전하래.

TextEng: Me just wants you to stop making trouble.
Text: 나 그냥 네가 문제 그만 만들면 좋겠어.

TextEng: Me look into plague, have questions.
Text: 나 역병 알아보는 중, 질문 있어.

TextEng: Me look for work.
Me need directions.
No need to get angry. I'll help you if I can.
No be angry. Me help you if me can.
No, I don't trust you.
Nope, me not trust you.
Hah! Forget it.
No way! You forget it.
And you should die... or, at least, Meldanen thinks so.
Text: 그리고 넌 죽어야 해... 아니면, 적어도 멜다넨은 그렇게 생각해.

TextEng: And you should be dying. Meldanen says hello.
Text: 그리고 넌 죽어야 해. 멜다넨이 안부 전하래.

TextEng: No, I'm here to kill you, instead. Meldanen sends his regards.
Text: 아니, 대신 널 죽이러 왔어. 멜다넨이 안부 전하래.

TextEng: Me kill you instead. Wizard says hello.
Text: 나 대신 너 죽여. 마법사가 안부 전하래.

TextEng: Yes, I do.
No, not yet.
No, and I don't intend to retrieve it, either.
Me has it.
No, me not have it.
No, and me not getting it, either.
Text: 아니, 그리고 나 안 가져올 거야.

TextEng: Then I shall get it.
All right, but I want my reward for the tooth now.
Text: 좋아, 하지만 이빨에 대한 보상은 먼저 줘.

TextEng: Forget it. Give me the reward for the tooth.
Me go and get it.
Okay, but me want reward for tooth now.
Text: 좋아, 근데 이빨 보상 지금 줘.

TextEng: No! Me just want reward for tooth!
Text: 안 돼! 나 이빨 보상만 원해!

TextEng: Fine. Then I shall get it for you.
Then I'll take my reward from your dead body!
Fine! Then I gets it!
Then me takes reward from you dead body!
Text: 그럼 네 죽은 몸에서 보상 내가 가져간다!

TextEng: He is dead. I have his silver tooth, here.
Text: 그는 죽었어. 여기 그의 은 이빨이 있어.

TextEng: He is dead, but I don't have his tooth.
Text: 그는 죽었지만, 그의 은 이빨은 없어.

TextEng: He lives, though not for long.
Text: 살아 있어, 하지만 오래 못 갈 거야.

TextEng: He lives, and I do not intend to kill him.
Text: 살아 있어, 그리고 죽일 생각도 없어.

TextEng: Dead. Me have silver tooth.
Dead, but me not have silver tooth.
Text: 죽었어, 근데 나 은 이빨 없어.

TextEng: He not dead, but me change that soon.
Text: 그 안 죽었어, 근데 나 곧 바꿀 거야.

TextEng: He not dead, and me not going to kill him.
Text: 그 안 죽었어, 그리고 나 죽일 생각 없어.

TextEng: Very well. I will return with the tooth.
Forget it. Let's just have this done with.
Okay, me come back with tooth.
Forget it. Me want this done with.
I was glad to help, but I don't want a reward for killing someone.
Text: 도와주게 되어 기뻤지만, 사람을 죽인 대가로는 보상받고 싶지 않아.

TextEng: Me glad to help, but me not want reward for killing.
Text: 나 도와서 기뻐, 근데 죽인 값 보상은 안 받아.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Getting the key was risky. Wouldn't some gold be fair?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 열쇠 얻는 건 위험했어. 금화 좀 더 주는 게 공평하지?

TextEng: No. Hand over more or I'll see how much *your* teeth are worth.
Text: 아니. 더 내놔, 아니면 네 이빨 값이 얼마나 되는지 보자고.

TextEng: It will do nicely.
I was glad to help. The reward is not necessary.
Text: 도와드리게 되어 기뻤습니다. 보상은 필요 없습니다.

TextEng: No, but I'll take everything off your corpse anyway.
Text: 아니, 하지만 어차피 네 시체에서 전부 챙길 거다.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me take big risk. Bigger reward is fairer, no?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 큰 위험 감수했어. 보상 더 큰 게 맞지, 안 그래?

TextEng: Nope. You give gold or me sell your teeth, maybe.
Text: 아니. 금화 더 줘, 아니면 네 이빨 팔아버릴지도.

TextEng: Is okay, I guess.
Me glad to help. Not need reward.
Text: 나 도와서 기뻐. 보상 필요 없어.

TextEng: Nah. Me take all gold from you dead body.
Text: 아니. 나 네 죽은 몸에서 금화 다 가져가.
